sql:
SELECT currency_name
FROM currencies
ORDER BY currency_name ASC;

external_knowledge:
- 'Binance API' is an Application Programming Interface for retrieving cryptocurrency data; 
- The time frame 'May 2023' refers to the dates between '2023-05-01' and '2023-06-01'; 
- An average exchange rate greater than 0.35 means that the value of one unit of the base currency is on average exchanged for more than 0.35 units of the quote currency.
